Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.91,0:27:17.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又來那麼大的…？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.67,0:27:18.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼哼
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.65,0:27:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什…
