Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.96,0:27:23.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千里山  升至第二名！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.28,0:27:27.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,碰
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.16,0:27:29.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了連莊的速攻嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.36,0:27:32.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼能讓你得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.37,0:27:34.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吃
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.83,0:27:35.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比速攻
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.06,0:27:38.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不會輸！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.67,0:27:40.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,立直
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.59,0:27:42.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,點和
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.76,0:27:43.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,3900點
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.30,0:27:46.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.57,0:27:49.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又用3900點的手牌遏制了我的立直啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.32,0:27:50.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.71,0:27:51.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.01,0:27:53.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,終於來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.33,0:28:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,終局…
